ighlights</h3>\n            <div class=\"project-grid\">\n                <div class=\"project-item\">\n                    <h4>Indie Film: \"Whispers in the Fog\"</h4>\n                    <p>Responsible for foley, dialogue editing, and atmospheric sound design, enhancing the suspenseful narrative.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\">Listen Sample</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"project-item\">\n                    <h4>Music Album: \"Midnight Bloom\" (Artist: Luna Echo)</h4>\n                    <p>Mixed and mastered the 10-track album, focusing on a warm analog feel and crisp vocal clarity.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\">Listen Sample</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"project-item\">\n                    <h4>Video Game: \"Galactic Odyssey\"</h4>\n                    <p>Designed and implemented all in-game sound effects and ambient audio, creating an engaging player experience.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\">Watch Gameplay w/ Sound</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"project-item\">\n                    <h4>Podcast Series: \"The History Uncovered\"</h4>\n                    <p>Provided full audio post-production, ensuring clear narration and a professional, polished sound.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#\">Listen Episode</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <h3>Skills</h3>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 1.1em;\"><strong>DAWs:</strong> Pro Tools, Logic Pro X, Ableton Live, Reaper<br>\n            <strong>Areas:</strong> Sound Design, Audio Editing, Mixing, Mastering, Foley, Field Recording, Live Sound Reinforcement</p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Anya Sharma. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <div class=\"contact-info\">\n                <a href=\"mailto:anya.sharma.audio@email.com